<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bienvenue — Ton espace d'intégration</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>

    <main class="page onboarding-page">
        <div id="loadingState" class="onboarding-loading">Chargement de ton espace…</div>

        <div id="errorState" class="onboarding-error hidden">
            <h2>Lien invalide ou expiré</h2>
            <p>Ce lien d'intégration n'existe pas ou a été révoqué. Contacte ton service RH pour en recevoir un nouveau.</p>
        </div>

        <div id="contentState" class="hidden">
            <section class="card welcome-card">
                <div id="empLogoSpace" class="welcome-logo-slot hidden"></div>
                <h2 class="welcome-title">Bienvenue, <span id="empWelcomeName" class="accent"></span> 👋</h2>
                <p class="welcome-sub">
                    Tu es attendu le <strong id="empWelcomeDate">—</strong> chez
                    <strong id="empWelcomeBoite"></strong>, en tant que
                    <em id="empWelcomePoste"></em>.
                </p>
                <div class="welcome-grid">
                    <div class="welcome-tile">
                        <span class="welcome-tile-label">Wi-Fi des bureaux</span>
                        <span id="empWelcomeWifi" class="welcome-tile-value mono">—</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="welcome-tile">
                        <span class="welcome-tile-label">Documents à consulter</span>
                        <div id="empDocsDownloadWrapper" class="welcome-docs">Aucun document annexe</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="card">
                <h3 class="card-title">Ton équipe</h3>
                <div id="teamContainer" class="team-list"></div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="app-footer">
        <p>© 2026 DayOne — Onboarding Cloud</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="onboarding.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
